      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.8/i686: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/e254f10a-dbf9-11e1-bfc4-52540035b04c).  Ran 10 tests.  No failures.",
