        ]
      },
      "date": "2016-11-16 22:19:44.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on el5/i686: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/af0dc7fa-da6d-11e1-b2f2-52540035b04c).  Ran 2 tests.  1 tests failed: lustre-initialization-1.",
